family_series.title: Family Series
family_series.description: Everything from cartoons to family comedies. Find your favorite shows and watch them all!

372424.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! Bonds Beyond Time
372424.description: For the first time, Yugi, Jaden and Yusei fight together against when a time traveler comes to destroy the Duel Monsters game!

484420.title: Casper the Friendly Ghost
484420.description: Casper and his buddies learn lessons about friendship and helping animals in this rare collection of cartoons perfect for children of all ages.

488979.title: Space Angel
488979.description: This space opera follows the adventures of an EBI (Earth Bureau of Investigation) agent as he saves the universe from various nefarious characters.

490046.title: Popeye and Friends (Vol. 1)
490046.description: Watch as America's favorite spinach-eating sailor, and his love, Olive Oyl, outsmart the bully Bluto, and share classic adventures.

490055.title: A Bucket Full of Cartoons
490055.description: Blast from the past collection for animation lovers with over ten of Paramount Studios’ vintage cartoon shorts from the late 1930s to the late 1940s.

584708.title: I Love Toy Trains: Ticket to Ride
584708.description: This best-selling, Parents' Choice award-winning series brings little ones all the locomotive action they crave in a large outdoor G-gauge exhibit.

673545.title: Hanna's Gold
673545.description: Two sisters find themselves on the adventure of a lifetime when they discover a long-lost treasure map on their father's horse ranch.

695900.title: The Adventure Club
695900.description: With the help of his friends, a young boy begins an adventure to find his fortune after the discovery of an ancient puzzle treasure box.

0300009663.title: The Adventures of Ozzie and Harriet
0300009663.description: A clean-cut 1950’s couple raises their two sons through life’s growing pains as they tackle issues surrounding teenage-hood, marriage and career.

0300006282.title: Zebra's Minecraft Fun: Zebra Gamer
0300006282.description: Get ready to join your friendly gamer guide as he explores the exciting world of Minecraft, which is ripe with imaginative creatures.

0300004818.title: GoGo Dino Explorers
0300004818.description: In the far reaches of the universe there is a planet called M25, on which many species exist, including dinosaurs that became extinct on earth thousands of years ago! Meet Rex, Tomo, Viki, Ping, and Rocky, the Gogo Dinos, whose mission is to explore M25, discovering new dinosaurs and always lending a helping hand to save the day!

0768.title: Gerry Anderson: Fireball XL5
0768.description: In the year 2062 the World Space Patrol watches the skies with its fleet of spacecraft.

01090.title: Inspector Gadget
01090.description: The bumbling Inspector Gadget, the worlds first bionic policeman, is equipped with an incredible array of gadgets to solve crime and save the day.

0300007502.title: Hard Hat Harry
0300007502.description: Join Hard Hat Harry, the loveable genie, for journeys' into the worlds of helicopters, construction, motorcycles, race cars, and many more.

0300007686.title: Matt Hatter Chronicles
0300007686.description: When little Matt finds a portal in his house to another dimension, he becomes the frontline of defense against villains trying to destroy the world.

04683.title: LEGO Nexo Knights
04683.description: Spells, magic, monsters and more unfold as the Knights from Knights’ Academy demonstrate their fighting prowess in the final graduation.

02100.title: Sonic X
02100.description: A malfunction sends Sonic the Hedgehog to Earth where he meets Chris, who helps collect Chaos Emeralds so Sonic and friends can go home.

01100.title: Sonic Underground
01100.description: Sonic, Manic and Sonia must fight Dr. Robotnik and his two sidekicks, Sleet and Dingo and the SWAT Bots, with the aid of their metal medallions and bring peace to Mobius and find mother!

0300010026.title: ALF Tales
0300010026.description: ALF and his friends from his home planet Melmac uniquely retell classic stories in this entertaining animated series for the whole family.

0300005753.title: Where's Chicky?
0300005753.description: When you're a baby chick navigating in a grown-up world, you meet new challenges with curiosity, excitement, and a spirit of adventure.

04706.title: LEGO Friends
04706.description: Five best friends go on some seriously cool LEGO adventures. Sometimes trouble happens and they get split up, but true friends are never far away.

03591.title: Chojin Sentai Jetman
03591.description: A freak accident leaves four unsuspecting humans with extraordinary powers. Now it's up to them to defend their dimension from villainous invaders.

01064.title: Tommy & Oscar
01064.description: The amazing adventures of Tommy, a ten-year-old child, and his friend Oscar, a music-eater creature from outer space.

0300006272.title: Zebra Gamer: Wii U Minecraft Super Mario Edition Gameplay
0300006272.description: Video game superfan Zebra Gamer takes on the Super Mario Mash-Up Pack for Minecraft Wii, a game that brings back iconic Super Mario World characters.

04833.title: Talking Tom Shorts
04833.description: When the precocious animated animals play silly games, laughter and good times are never far away, and adventures are ready to be had.

04377.title: Strawberry Shortcake
04377.description: A birthday celebration for Apple Dumpling, a trip to the North Pole to find gifts for Strawberry Shortcake's friends, the search for Spring, a get-well party for Honey Pie Pony are designed to bring the charm of Strawberry Shortcake to a new generation of children.

04305.title: The Country Mouse and the City Mouse Adventures
04305.description: Join level-headed country mouse Emily, and her fancy city cousin, Alexander, as they explore and solve mysteries using their sleuth instincts.

04834.title: Talking Tom and Friends
04834.description: Meet Angela, Ben, Hank, and Ginger, a team of tech-savvy friends who are always ready to laugh and have some exciting adventures together.

01008.title: DC Nation Shorts
01008.description: A series of shorts featuring characters from DC Comics including Thunder and Lightning, Green Arrow, Lego Batman, Metal Men, Shazam! and more!

02067.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!
02067.description: Follows the adventures of teenager Yugi, whose magical secret comes to life when he plays his favorite card game: 'Duel Monsters.'

0300007148.title: The Cat in the Hat Knows a Lot About That!
0300007148.description: The Cat in The Hat knows a lot about virtually every thing. With the help of fish, thing 1, and thing 2; the Cat in the Hat teaches kids about many things through song and games.

02121.title: Eloise: Me, Eloise
02121.description: An animated series for children based on the classic "Eloise at the Plaza" books from the 1950's written by Kay Thompson and illustrated by Hilary Knight.

04844.title: The New Scooby-Doo Mysteries
04844.description: Ruh-roh! Scooby-Doo, Scrappy, and the Mystery Machine gang are together again to solve a new batch of exciting, spooky, and brain-puzzling mysteries.

0300006745.title: Jakers! The Adventures of Piggley Winks
0300006745.description: Get lost in a grandfather pig’s imaginative stories that take us on the exciting adventures of a youthful pig and his two best friends.

03669.title: Science Max
03669.description: Everyday science experiments get supersized and turbocharged in this fun children's series that takes learning to a whole new level.

0300006518.title: Om Nom Stories
0300006518.description: Based on the "Cut the Rope" video game, follow our small green monster friend as he lives a life full of hilarious and entertaining adventures.

013.title: GI Joe Renegades
013.description: On the run after being accused of crimes they didn't commit, six young G.I.s battle to cleair their names - and expose the real bad guys, COBRA Industries!

04295.title: Archie's Weird Mysteries
04295.description: Archie and the Riverdale gang head into strange turf after a school lab experiment goes wrong and weird things come to town.

02923.title: The Big Comfy Couch
02923.description: The Big Comfy Couch is about a little clown named Loonette and her doll Molly with their Big Comfy couch. The couch has everything known to man inside it - be it an umbrella, a hat, or a kitchen sink! Co-stars include Granny Garbanzo, Auntie Macassar, and Major Bedhead, who pops in for visits. And unbeknownst to Loonette, two dustbunnies, Fuzzy and Wuzzy, live under Loonette's couch.

0300008692.title: Horrible Histories
0300008692.description: An intrepid trio learns valuable lessons with help from famous characters of the past in this animated series based on Terry Deary’s Scholastic books.

0300008198.title: Are We There Yet?
0300008198.description: A divorced mother marries a former athlete, creating a hilarious and often chaotic blended household, where squabbles are always overcome by love.

0300009158.title: MasterChef Junior
0300009158.description: Talented children between the ages of 8 and 13 showcase their culinary abilities and passion for food through a series of delicious challenges.

04699.title: LEGO Chima
04699.description: It’s a rescue mission of truly epic proportions when the animal tribes of Chima stand united and travel into the dangerous Outlands.

03135.title: Kyuukyuu Sentai GoGoFive
03135.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! After the Bowzock, a ruthless-not to mention reckless- gang of interstellar biker thugs, destroy his home planet of Hazard, Dappu visits Earth where he discovers five humans with the ability to harness "Carmagic." With this power, these five heroes can defeat the Bowzock before the band of witless bikers is able to add Earth to its list of wrecked worlds.

04718.title: LEGO Ninjago Masters of Spinjitzu
04718.description: Peace has returned to Ninjago, but the four ninja warriors swear to protect and learn to master their Golden Weapons awaiting Lord Garmadon's return.

01074.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero Mini Series
01074.description: The GI Joe Special Missions force must battle to build a counter-weapon to Cobra's teleportation device.

0300006271.title: Sneaky Stripes Minecraft Gameplay: Zebra Gamer
0300006271.description: The popular video game fan, known on YouTube as Zebra Gamer, takes viewers through 15 different levels of Minecraft Co-Op with his best friend.

03456.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL
03456.description: Aspiring duelist Yuma and strange visitor Astral team up so Yuma can learn the art of the duel while Astral gets the help he needs to regain his memories.

02362.title: Sam & Max
02362.description: Sam & Max are freelance police and view the world as their own personal theme park.

0300004999.title: Garfield and Friends
0300004999.description: Lazy, lasagna-loving cat Garfield has fun adventures with his pal Odie and owner Jon.

0300006371.title: One Stormy Night
0300006371.description: After a chaotic experience, a sheep and a wolf become pals. The next morning, they must decide what to do with their unlikely friendship.

0300005118.title: YooHoo & Friends
0300005118.description: The cute and cuddly YooHoo and friends are back to save their village and keep their fountain of youth safe from a boss who wants to sell it for cash.

0300006778.title: Barney & Friends
0300006778.description: Gather your little ones around to hear from the friendliest purple dinosaur, who has a passion for learning with his favorite friends!

0300009755.title: Ariel & Zoey & Eli, Too
0300009755.description: A series following sibling-musicians Ariel, Zoey, and Eli, as they write songs, perform musical numbers and interview accomplished artists.

0203.title: Wild at Heart
0203.description: A British veterinarian and his family relocate to the African Heartland to take on the challenges of running a wild game reserve.

01088.title: Hurray for Huckle!
01088.description: Curiosities are everywhere in Busytown and so are Huckle Cat, Lowly Worm, Sally Cat, Hilda Hippo plus Pig Will and Pig Wont. Each episode is an innovative blend of humor and learning based around six unforgettable friends and manyother colorful characters from the amazing world of Richard Scarrys books.

04832.title: Talking Tom Heroes
04832.description: When the adorable animated gang receives a few powerful crystals and gadgets, they become brave, emboldened superheroes ready to save the day!

0300007026.title: Beyblade: Metal Fusion
0300007026.description: The Beyblade franchise lets it rip in this series about a kid looking to his secretive past for clues while fighting for good against evil foes.

0300007845.title: My Dad the Rock Star
0300007845.description: The very reserved son of a fun-loving, metal rocker Dad who wears theatrical makeup and has green hair tries to lead as normal life as he can.

0300009731.title: The Red Green Show
0300009731.description: This series follows hapless handyman Red Green as he welcomes viewers to Canada, where he and other colorful characters film a do-it-yourself TV show.

04364.title: SheZow
04364.description: An extreme 12-year-old with an attitude inherits his late aunt’s ring and turns him into a female superhero with comic results.

01094.title: Mona The Vampire
01094.description: Mona Parker isnt really a vampire; she is a little girl with a big imagination. She constantly imagines herself facing ghosts, zombies and every other monster you can think of, putting on her cape and glow in the dark fangs to become  what else  Mona the Vampire!

09.title: GI Joe: A Real American Hero
09.description: Together they defend the globe against Cobra, a ruthless organization led by Serpentor and the recently rejuvenated Cobra Commander, who are both determined to conquer the world by any means necessary.

0562.title: Wayside
0562.description: Anything can happen in a school that was all mixed up the day it was built.

0300007098.title: Little Charmers
0300007098.description: A hip animation that welcomes you to a world of magic and imagination. With a little patience, determination and a flick of their magic wands, anything is possible.

04731.title: Sandra: The Fairytale Detective
04731.description: With help from her loyal elf sidekick, a kid descendant from a long line of fairytale sleuths solves mysteries in the Land of Once Upon a Time.

0300008154.title: Voltron Force
0300008154.description: Five robotic lions piloted by the Voltron Force come together to form a super robot that fights against evil, taking down one bad guy at a time.

011.title: Transformers: Generation 1
011.description: Sentient robotic beings from Cybertron crash land on Earth, divided into two factions – the Autobots and Decepticons – as they both vie for Energon!

0300010076.title: Eight Is Enough
0300010076.description: This touching series follows a close-knit family as they face the hardships and challenges of the ups and downs of everyday life in a family of ten.

01091.title: King
01091.description: Shortly after moving into a new house, 12 year- old Russell discovers something weird under his bed - a trap door leading to the fantastic world of Under! Russell is crowned King of Under, and boy, does his kingdom need help!

0300000124.title: Gilligan's Island
0300000124.description: Shipwrecked on an uncharted South Pacific island, seven castaways struggle to survive the outdoors—and each other—in this wacky classic comedy series.

02.title: Jem
02.description: Using holograms, Jerrica and her pals become Jem and the Holograms, battling other bands like the Misfits and the Stingers, to keep the Starlight foundation going!

0300005083.title: Adventures of Sonic the Hedgehog
0300005083.description: Sonic the Hedgehog and his faithful sidekick Tails race to prevent the despicable Dr. Robotnik from enslaving the population of Planet Mobius.

01495.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's
01495.description: New Domino City, the playground to legendary duelist Yugi Muto, has been transformed into a futuristic society where dueling has kicked into overdrive.

05.title: Transformers Energon
05.description: Years after "Transformers Armada", the Autobots continue to battle the Decepticons to prevent the resurrection of Unicron.

04619.title: PAC-MAN and the Ghostly Adventures
04619.description: Pac and his buds try to get the hang of being teenagers enlisted to protect Pac-World from a ghostly army led by the evil Betrayus.

0300007068.title: The Worst Witch
0300007068.description: Accident-prone Mildred Hubble is the worst witch that Miss Cackle's Academy for Witches has ever known. She can't ride her broomstick without crashing, her spells are always going spectacularly wrong and even her cat isn't regulation black. But Mildred manages to struggle by until she gets on the wrong side of Miss Hardbroom and spiteful teacher's pet Ethel Hallow (Felicity Jones).

02180.title: Chouriki Sentai Ohranger
02180.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! It is the year 1999. The Machine Empire of Baranoia, led by Emperor Bacchus Wrath, has invaded Earth with the intention of wiping out all human life and bringing about machine rule. Chief Counsellor Miura of the UAOH (United Airforce Overtech Hardware), in a desperate attempt to quell this invasion, has revived super energies born of the lost civilization of Pangaea. Enlisting an elite squad of the finest officers the UAOH has to offer, Miura has harnessed Tetrahedron Power, granting the team the power to transform into the Ohrangers, and save humanity from its darkest crisis yet!

0300007778.title: The Hilarious House of Frightenstein
0300007778.description: This classic children’s comedy show about the mishaps and learning curves of Count Frightenstein and his wacky friends in exile at Frankenstone.

02403.title: Spliced!
02403.description: Dr. Moreau finally achieved his goal of creating an island populated by prototype mutant animals: all spliced, and warped into new and bizarre forms.

021.title: Transformers: Prime
021.description: Roll out with all-new adventures starring Optimus Prime, Bumblebee, Arcee, and the rest of the heroic Autobots as they battle the evil Decepticons! Now that big bad Megatron has returned to Earth, Team Prime prepares for an epic struggle to save the planet. Meanwhile, the Autobots have to guard Jack, Miko, and Raf, three kids who've accidentally discovered them. Intense drama, heavy metal action, awesome animation--it's all here, bigger and better than ever!

0300007046.title: Flight 29 Down
0300007046.description: The story of seven kids lost on a deserted island in the Pacific Ocean.

018.title: Transformers: Animated
018.description: The Decepticons have appeared in Detroit, and it's up to the Autobots to stop Megatron and his evil plans!

0538.title: GI Joe - Sigma Six
0538.description: SIGMA 6 is the code name for a new group of covert GI JOE operatives with highly specialized capabilities.

0300007711.title: Charmers
0300007711.description: A teenager attends a summer camp where she connects with a coven of friendly teen witches out to defeat a demon haunting their campgrounds.

0300006835.title: Sandokan
0300006835.description: The exciting adventures of a tiger pirate and his hilarious crew, as they attempt to recover hidden treasures located all over the world.

0300008640.title: Love, Diana by pocket.watch
0300008640.description: Join your imaginative hosts Diana and Roma as they go on magical adventures where learning is fun and anything is possible if you work together!

0300010302.title: Too Cute!
0300010302.description: This series tells the coming-of-age stories of cuddly baby animals, from their wobbly first steps to their first venture into the outside world.

01117.title: Super Sentai Zyuranger
01117.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! Ky_ry_ Sentai Zyuranger is a Japanese tokusatsu television series and the sixteenth installment in the long-running Super Sentai franchise of superhero programs.

03455.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX
03455.description: Follow a new generation of duelists at the prestigious Duel Academy—a highly competitive boarding school where pencils and books have been replaced by Duel Disks and monster cards!

0300006666.title: Tobot
0300006666.description: Heroic twin brothers share a big secret: They protect their city by piloting advanced, transforming cars that battle a growing throng of villains.

0300006855.title: Scooby-Doo and Scrappy-Doo
0300006855.description: Everyone’s favorite mystery-solving Great Dane is here to find clues, along with a little help from his energetic nephew and four human companions.

01583.title: My Little Pony Original Series
01583.description: Ponyland is a mystical land, home to all kinds of magical creatures. The Little Ponies make their home in Paradise Estate, living a peaceful life filled with song and games. However, not all of the creatures of Ponyland are so peaceful, and the Ponies often find themselves having to fight for survival against witches, trolls, goblins and all the other beasts that would love to see the Little Ponies destroyed, enslaved or otherwise harmed.

0300004890.title: Suckers
0300004890.description: Learn all about the dreams, fears and ambitions of the naughty and mischievous Suckers.

02409.title: Ultraman Leo
02409.description: Alien intergalactic slavers called Magma come to Earth in an attempt to find more slaves for their expanding evil empire. In response, the Ultra Warriors send Leo to protect the planet from this new threat.

01085.title: Dino Squad
01085.description: Five quirky Teens suddenly gain powers to transform into Dinosaurs, they find out that high school is only one of the battles they'll have to face.

0300004899.title: Some Assembly Required
0300004899.description: A 14-year-old running a toy company hires a group of his friends to help him create amazing new toys.

01087.title: Horseland
01087.description: Five friends and their amazing horses ride together through the ups and downs of being a kid in the incredible stable known as Horseland.

0300008447.title: Dear America
0300008447.description: Meet American history’s standout young women, who represented the values of their time, as well as a spirit of determination and perseverance.

0300005229.title: Pucca
0300005229.description: Follow the reckless antics of a feisty noodle shop delivery girl and her reluctant ninja master crush, Garu.

0300008446.title: The Baby-Sitters Club
0300008446.description: The beloved story of a young girl and her group of friends as they share their struggles balancing school work, babysitting, and growing up.

02262.title: Dance Academy
02262.description: Fifteen-year-old Tara Webster has grown up on a farm in country Australia and has dreamt of being a dancer ever since she was a little girl. When she makes it into the National Academy of Dance - the best school in the country - she is sure her life is about to be spectacular. What Tara doesn't realise is how far behind she is in her training, and that there's a whole lot more to surviving the Academy than just dancing...

0300006332.title: Crazy Craft Minecraft Survival (Sigils)
0300006332.description: Join your favorite gamer friends as they take on the thrilling world of Crazy Craft, also known as the most unpredictable Minecraft Mod Pack.

0300005087.title: Lockie Leonard
0300005087.description: Facing another year in the middle of nowhere, surf rat Lockie makes the best of small-town life with his friends and semi-functional family.

0944.title: Gerry Anderson: Thunderbirds
0944.description: Operating from a top-secret island base in the year 2065, the team at International Rescue- intrepid Jeff Tracy and his valiant sons Scott, John, Virgil, Gordon, and Alan- engage in a never-ending humanitarian crusade to protect the innocent.

04243.title: Rainbow Ruby
04243.description: You can always count on the ever-courageous Rainbow Ruby to rescue her doll friends, and take a magical journey into Rainbow Village.

0300008888.title: Kid-E-Cats
0300008888.description: A trio of enthusiastic kittens are ready to approach any adventure with their signature high energy antics and paw-sitively delightful attitudes.

0300008173.title: The Daltons
0300008173.description: Four brothers attempt to bust out of jail in this hilarious animated series that depicts creativity, ingenuity, and some good ol’ physical comedy!

0300006192.title: Metalions
0300006192.description: The gadgets left behind by his scientist grandfather sends an 8-year-old on a journey with an ancient warrior to find a set of Earth-saving stones.

0300004700.title: Camp Lakebottom
0300004700.description: A little boy gets on the wrong bus for summer camp, befriending two other kids before they end up at a weird, adventurous camp with a new enemy.

04749.title: The Aquabats! Super Show!
04749.description: A rock band consisting of five superheroes battle monsters in a retro campy style, complete with fake commercials and the heroes in cartoon form.

01585.title: Beast Machines: Transformers
01585.description: The Maximals awaken on their home planet of Cybertron and are chased by mindless Vehicons created by Megatron. The Maximals must free the planet from Megatron and restore it to its real way of living.

04048.title: Barney Google & Snuffy Smith
04048.description: Animated series, based on the classic cartoon strip, about a hilariously feisty and cranky band of family and friends living in the backwoods hills.

0300007561.title: Animal Atlas
0300007561.description: Get to know members of the diverse animal kingdom in this educational program, which encourages viewers to protect these amazing creatures.

0300007049.title: Zig & Sharko: At the Beach
0300007049.description: A desert island, a starving hyena and one obsession: eat the mermaid! This season, his dream might even come true… she set up house on the beach! Problem: so has her bodyguard, the shark! Ouch!

03035.title: Kid's Animated History With Pipo
03035.description: Using the Time Compass, funny-bone tickler Pipo guides kids on adventures in history, travelling everywhere from ancient Egypt to classical Greece.

0300007636.title: Sarah & Duck
0300007636.description: Meet Sarah, seven years old, with big eyes and a green hat who lives with her quacky, flappy best friend, Duck. Sarah and Duck live in a small village, in a small house, with a small, wonky garden path and a red front door. Together they embark on simple but exciting adventures, exploring their world both near and far in their own wobbly and imaginative way, joined by friends and neighbours including Small Scared Bug and Scarf Lady.

01794.title: The Woodlies: The Series
01794.description: The Woodlies – made up of Curious Nineeyes, fearless Firehead and gentle Sevenpoints - are small troll-like creatures who live in harmony alongside us human ‘uglies’. They notice their tummies begin to rumble at the onset of autumn and set forth to scavenge food from the nearby camp ground. But in a nearby swamp, a menacing gang of Woodlies called ‘Swamp Rats’ also have food on their mind...and will stop at nothing to take what’s not rightfully theirs. The Woodlies soon find themselves disbanded, lost and on the menu of various predators who hungrily await to eat Woodlie for tea! What ensures is a battle for survival in the depths of a harsh winter - but not without plenty of comic difficulty at every turn!

03042.title: Seijuu Sentai Gingaman
03042.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! Three millennia after the first invasion of the Space Pirates Barban, a new set of Gingamen - Hyuuga, Gouki, Hayate, Hikaru, Saya - have been selected to protect the Earth. That is, unless the Barban are able to disrupt the ceremony!

01546.title: Wolfblood
01546.description: Being a teen is hard but being a Wolfblood is even more complicated as Maddy and the others try to keep their shape-shifting secret from the world.

04378.title: Space Ranger Roger
04378.description: Join one brave little alien, who leads a team of rowdy Ranger Bots, as they assist their loyal Earth friends in need of rescue from various foes.

0300006856.title: The Flintstones
0300006856.description: Laugh along with the classic misadventures of two modern-day Stone Age families living amongst dinosaurs, doing their best in prehistoric times.

0300009206.title: Black Hole High
0300009206.description: Five kids and their science teacher have a variety of preternatural adventures at a mysterious boarding school, Blake Holsey High.

0300009481.title: Snow Queen
0300009481.description: A young woman must journey through the seasons to rescue her boyfriend who has been kidnapped by the evil Snow Queen in this heartwarming love story.

04829.title: The 13 Ghosts of Scooby-Doo
04829.description: When everyone’s favorite mystery solving Great Dane opens a mysterious box, he accidentally unleashes a series of frightening spirits.

0300006437.title: Toca Life Stories
0300006437.description: Four pals take on a variety of fun-filled adventures, like petting the tiniest of animals, overcoming stagefright, and trying all kinds of new stuff.

0300008373.title: Animorphs
0300008373.description: When Earth has been invaded by a race of mind-controlling aliens, it’s up to five teenagers and their ability to morph into animals to save humanity.

01607.title: Cool McCool
01607.description: Cool McCool foils the dastardly deed of wacky criminals in an outrageous assortment of cartoon adventures bursting with cloak-and-dagger lunacy. Theres no short supply of kooky cases, McCool knows exactly how to uncover lots of laughs.

0300009785.title: The Choo Choo Bob Show
0300009785.description: Join your host and his pals while they hang out in the Bobville Clubhouse awaiting their next adventure through the fascinating world of trains.

015.title: Littlest Pet Shop
015.description: Blythe lives in the big city, right above the Littlest Pet Shop, a day-camp for all types of pets. When she discovers she can talk to the animals, the adventure begins!

02361.title: Redwall
02361.description: A tale of a wondrous quest to recover a legendary lost weapon, and of the friendship between Matthias and Cornflower who helps him to realize that a big heart and courage can be more useful than brute strength.

0563.title: Willa's Wild Life
0563.description: This 9-year-old critter collector has adopted a giraffe, a couple elephants, an alligator and so many other exotic animals, theres barely room in Willas room for Willa!

0300008297.title: BoBoiBoy
0300008297.description: A boy with elemental powers, who can separate into three, his robot sidekick, and his pals fight evil aliens, who try to invade Earth for cocoa beans.

0300009145.title: Gulliver's Travels
0300009145.description: A seafaring 18th-century Englishman returns home with extraordinary tales of fantastic lands, and must prove his sanity to rescue his wife and son.

02066.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V
02066.description: Yuya Sakaki’s dream is and become the greatest “duel-tainer” in history, like his father, and he just might pull it off!

0300005863.title: Little Lizard Gaming: Minecraft Dragons!
0300005863.description: Join Little Lizard for Minecraft dragon adventures and gets tips and tricks on the hit video game,

010.title: Transformers: Armada
010.description: It's up to Optimus and the Autobots to stop Megatron from turning all robots on Earth into Decepticons with the Allspark!

01089.title: In the Night Garden
01089.description: In The Night Garden is about a magical picture-book place that exists between waking and sleeping in a childs imagination. Reached by following a magical little blue star, the Night Garden is a warm and affectionate world which is home to a comical and diverse community of toys, living happily together and who care for each other unconditionally.

02280.title: Anatole
02280.description: A loving husband and father to six charming children from outside of Paris, Anatole acts as an ambassador between the mouse world and the human world.

02927.title: Gekisou Sentai Carranger
02927.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! After the Bowzock, a ruthless-not to mention reckless- gang of interstellar biker thugs, destroy his home planet of Hazard, Dappu visits Earth where he discovers five humans with the ability to harness "Carmagic." With this power, these five heroes can defeat the Bowzock before the band of witless bikers is able to add Earth to its list of wrecked worlds.

0464.title: Gerry Anderson: Stingray
0464.description: The flagship of the World Aquanaut Security Patrol (W.A.S.P.), Stingray is the world's most highly sophisticated submarine, capable of speeds of over 600 knots and the ability to submerge to the very bottom of the Earth's oceans. Under the command of the square-jawed and heroic Captain Troy Tempest, Stingray explores the most treacherous depths of our waters and protects the world from the perils that lurk undersea.

02311.title: The Saddle Club
02311.description: Amid the excitement and thrill of the horse world, growing up seems harder than ever; but together, the Saddle Club girls are ready to take on the world. From finding the courage to compete in a major horse show in front of hundreds of people, to surviving that first broken heart, the Saddle Club girls overcome seemingly insurmountable obstacles. Stevie, Lisa and Carole struggle to support one another through the inevitable joys and sorrows associated with becoming teenagers.

01093.title: Magi-Nation
01093.description: Young Tony Jones is an average teen from Earth who finds himself mysteriously transported to the magical world of Magi-Nation.  In these Moonlands Tony befriends two young Magi heroes-in-training who join him on a journey to defeat the evil Shadow Magi who are out to rule their world.  Along with their trusty collection of Dream Creatures these new friends must solve riddles, battle evil and discover the secrets hidden in each region on the Moonlands.

0300005010.title: Worst Year of My Life, Again!
0300005010.description: A teenager reliving a horrible high school year filled with bullying and humiliation attempts to get things right this time.

0300007121.title: Yo Gabba Gabba!
0300007121.description: Yo Gabba Gabba! is a fun live-action program for young children ages 1 and up. Join our host DJ Lance Rock as he introduces us to friendly toy monsters in a magical land full of music, dance, colorful cartoons and simple life lessons that will get you and your children up off the floor to learn and dance along.

0300006836.title: The Untouchables of Elliot Mouse
0300006836.description: Set in 1930 “Cheescago,” this is the story of one brave mouse who must stand up to kingpin Al Catone and his wicked feline cronies.

04669.title: Guess How Much I Love You: The Adventures of Little Nutbrown Hare
04669.description: A beloved, award-winning animated series about a father hare and his son who live in a watercolor landscape of forests, rivers and warm life lessons.

0300007186.title: Roblox Funny Moments (MrQuackerJack)
0300007186.description: MrQuackerJack is having adventures in Roblox! Check out his Funny Moment Adventures as he explores games with his best friend PairofDucks.

02298.title: Funpak
02298.description: FunPak is a collection of creator driven animated shorts developed and produced by Nelvana's celebrated studio talent.

0300007093.title: Scaredy Squirrel
0300007093.description: Join Scaredy; a lovable, and nerdy hero, as he tackles daily challenges stacking cans at the Stash n' Hoard grocery store.

02041.title: Ninja Sentai Kakuranger
02041.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! The day has arrived and it is up to the Kakurangers, along with the Three God Generals, to defeat the Youkais, before Daimaou's villainy destroys Earth!

04106.title: Ninpuu Sentai Hurricaneger
04106.description: After tragedy strikes on graduation day at the Ninja Academy, three pupils waste no time taking on the clan of evil space warriors responsible.

0300008168.title: World Pet Games
0300008168.description: Contestants place their pets in five hilarious, adorable events where winners get a donation to an animal charity made in their honor.

0300009564.title: Skippy
0300009564.description: Follow the adventures of Sonny and his kangaroo, Skippy, who live in Waratah National Park in New South Wales where Sonny's dad is the park ranger.

0300007048.title: Zig & Sharko: The Laugh Boat
0300007048.description: Marina takes her friends aboard an ocean liner for a cruise around the world. But it’s not vacation time for her and Sharko...with a famished hyena on board, danger is always lurking over the next wave!

02063.title: Monkey See Monkey Do
02063.description: An animated and live action preschool series that educates kids about animals and their natural habitats through the use of engaging song and dance! Follow Monkey and his buddy Parrot, as they invite kids to get up off the couch and join in the “wild” fun, imitating the behaviour and movement of cool creatures from around the world; while also learning the importance of friendship along the way!

0300006777.title: Angelina Ballerina
0300006777.description: A nervous 8-year-old mouse faces her fears at a new school, where she has to learn to embrace music and dance to express herself.

017.title: Pound Puppies
017.description: A team of fearless dogs is on a mission to find homes for puppies in need. Once you're a pound puppy, you're always a pound puppy!

0300005157.title: Super Wings
0300005157.description: The action-packed preschool series features an adorable jet, who travels the world with his amazing plane pals, delivering packages to kids.

0300007657.title: 800 Words
0300007657.description: A comfortable Australian journalist becomes a single father when his wife dies and soon decides to move with his two kids to New Zealand to regroup.

0300010075.title: Daktari
0300010075.description: A veterinarian and his daughter fend off poachers, diamond smugglers, and big-game hunters while running an animal study center in East Africa.

0300004893.title: My Big Big Friend
0300004893.description: Yuri, Lili and Matt are brought together by the power of their imaginations and their very own Big, Big Friends.

04808.title: HobbyKids Adventures
04808.description: Three brothers fly, bounce, and zoom through the day, using fun, food, and cool  inventions to foil their enemies and make the world a better place.

0300004947.title: The Girl From Tomorrow
0300004947.description: A 13-year-old girl from the year 3000 is stranded in the modern world and must battle a fugitive warlord for a time capsule to return home.

02265.title: Kung Fu Masters of the Zodiac
02265.description:
When an evil spirit dead-set on conquering the world rises from the beyond, the star gods send a young boy
named Polaris to defeat the spirit and maintain peace. As Polaris trains to become a powerful warrior, he
must learn from 12 Kung Fu Masters before facing off against his ultimate foe, in this animated action adventure

0300009596.title: Adina's Deck
0300009596.description: This award-winning technology and Internet safety video series are for families to help pre-teens better understand the social side of technology.

0300007032.title: 6teen
0300007032.description: This sharp and amusing mid-00s animated comedy follows the after-school lives of six 16 year-old mall-rats.

04508.title: Mani
04508.description: Sky's parents hire an unconventional nanny who forms an unlikely bond with the young girl as he helps her learn important life lessons.

01098.title: Sabrina: The Animated Series
01098.description: In the town of Greendale lives Sabrina, a half mortal and half witch who often uses spells to wreak middle school havoc.

02176.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
02176.description: Bean is back! Join him, alongside his best friend Teddy and his long-suffering landlady, for more zany mishaps that surround his daily life.

04304.title: Cake
04304.description: This clever show-within-a-show follows a teen girl named Cake, who hosts a cable access show about making everyday items extraordinary.

03330.title: Bruno the Kid
03330.description: A boy genius goes on dangerous missions as the world's youngest spy, while trying to keep his side job hidden from his parents and classmates.

02406.title: Wild C.A.T.S.
02406.description: The benevolent race known as the Wild C.A.T.s (Covert Action Team), are fearless, super-powered warriors sworn to defeat the evil Daemonites, who seek to dominate planet Earth.

0539.title: Beast Wars
0539.description: On pliocenic Earth, the heroic Maximals and the evil Predacons battle for survival against each other and against a violent planet.

0300005002.title: Steve and Maggie
0300005002.description: Steve and his friend Maggie Magpie invite children to join them in their fun and amazing approach to learning English through music and video stories.

0300006913.title: Dr. Panda
0300006913.description: When our friendly panda hero encounters a problem he doesn’t know how to solve, he relies on his friends, creativity, and imagination to fix it!

0855.title: Clue
0855.description: Follow six young sleuths as they witness a crime and embark on a mysterious adventure they never could have imagined!

0300008777.title: My Magic Theater
0300008777.description: Here is a paper-puppetry show for kids, featuring classic fairytales such as Cinderella, Snow White, The Little Mermaid, and more.

0300000119.title: The Facts of Life
0300000119.description: Four teens, each with their own backgrounds and personalities, become inseparable friends when they’re brought together at Eastland Academy for girls.

04242.title: Rev and Roll
04242.description: When 8-year-old Rev teams up with his best friend and powerful truck, Rumble, there’s nothing they can’t do. Join them for fun adventures.

03535.title: Fish N Chips
03535.description: An impressionable young fish and his lifelong enemy, a mischievous cat, go on hilarious, exciting adventures across both land and sea.

01790.title: Tashi
01790.description: When Jack’s parents bundle him off to stay with his distant cousin Tashi, the two boys get swept up in a series of wild adventures exploring a fantastic land far, far away, and protecting Tashi’s village from a host of creatures and villains. In a strange new world, where nothing seems familiar and your logic doesn’t work, how do you survive and thrive? Luckily for city slicker Jack, his new best friend Tashi is the perfect guide through this exotic, upside down, crazy world. And the boys can always depend on warm and whimsical Lotus Blossom to help them navigate any tricky situation! Giants, ghosts, witches, bandits, demons, dragons... Tashi, Jack and Lotus Blossom are ready for anything!

0300005607.title: Zig & Sharko: In the Lagoon
0300005607.description: The misadventures on a deserted island between a wily hyena hungry for a mermaid dinner and the musclebound shark who is her protective best friend.

03072.title: The Adventures of Swiss Family Robinson
03072.description: The further family adventures of the Robinsons, a shipwrecked family who must struggle together to make a new life on a remote, desert island.

0303.title: Dennis the Menace
0303.description: The Comic misadventures of television's most well-meaning but misguided boy are back. The lovable Dennis Mitchell left a trail of chaos throughout his suburban neighborhood, yet managed to pry his way into the hearts of millions from week to week.

0300006330.title: Story Mode Minecraft Season Two Gameplay: Zebra Gamer
0300006330.description: Join an excitable gamer as he prepares to explore all throughout the Minecraft world, where great adventures and epic conquests await the daring.

0300007410.title: Car City Super: Baby Trucks
0300007410.description: Join Car City’s adorable automotive infants Chili, Sunny, and Berry Every as they tool around their metropolis learning and meeting its residents.

03696.title: Hyakujuu Sentai Gaoranger
03696.description: Five color-coded warriors are called upon to protect Earth from the monstrous Orgs, who have reignited their war on humanity after a long silence.

04.title: Transformers Cybertron
04.description: The Autobots embark on a quest to locate mystical artifacts to save their homeworld of Cybertron from being sucked into a black hole.

0300007455.title: Rocky Jones, Space Ranger
0300007455.description: Captain Rocky Jones and his fellow Rangers, pretty Vera and 10-year-old Bobby, patrol the United Worlds of the Solar System and stamp out evil.

01622.title: Naruto (Subtitled)
01622.description: 12 years ago, the Nine-Tailed Fox claimed many lives before its spirit was contained with a baby boy who has now grown to become a ninja-in-training.

0300006462.title: Camp Minecraft Survival (Sigils)
0300006462.description: Laugh along with popular gamer Sigils and his friends, as they tap into the Camp Minecraft Server for hilarious moments and epic fails.

0300010161.title: Fireside Reading of a Study in Scarlet
0300010161.description: Experience A Study in Scarlet like never before. Gildart Jackson's cozy fireside reading of the classic tale can be enjoyed by all ages.

0300007764.title: Pokémon the Series: Black & White
0300007764.description: Ash and Pikachu are off to the distant Unova region, where they'll encounter new friends, new rivals, new challenges, and all-new Pokémon! Upon arrival, Ash meets aspiring Dragon Master Iris, full of spirit and determination, and Pokémon Connoisseur Cilan, who is always available to lend his expertise. Above all, Ash will need plenty of new Pokémon on his team if he wants to win Unova's tournaments and Gym badges. Following his every move is the criminal trio of Team Rocket, with sinister new schemes and a fresh resolve to catch Pikachu! Then there's the mysterious N...is he a friend or a foe, and what is his connection with the secret organization known as Team Plasma? And what is Team Plasma planning to do with one of the Legendary Pokémon of the Unova region? Once this adventure starts, the excitement won't stop!

03349.title: Super Mario World
03349.description: King Koopa is on the loose, and he's ready to battle the Super Mario Bros. using a powerful new weapon: his own children!

02308.title: Denji Sentai Megaranger
02308.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! When his video game prowess is discovered by I.N.E.T., high school student Kenta Date is brought in to lend his expertise to their mysterious research. Meanwhile, four classmates show up, wanting to know more about the I.N.E.T. facility. Their experience will change their lives forever, as I.N.E.T. survives an attack by the nefarious Dr. Hinelar and an army from another dimension determined to conquer our reality!

03367.title: C.O.P.S
03367.description: A ruthless kingpin rules Empire City, and it's up to a courageous FBI agent and his squad of superpowered cops to make a better tomorrow.

0300005056.title: Mortified
0300005056.description: An imaginative young girl uses her vivid creativity to fantasize and escape the pressures of school and avoid the embarrassment of her parents.
